00:06:23.349 --> 00:06:23.983
Absolutely.

00:06:23.983 --> 00:06:24.684
And in essence,

00:06:24.684 --> 00:06:25.351
what we're talking about,

00:06:25.351 --> 00:06:27.153
Boris here is conditioning the aide

00:06:27.153 --> 00:06:29.155
